title: We Will Rock You
author: Queen
lyrics:
[00:13.16] Buddy, you're a boy, make a big noise
[00:15.42] Playing in the street, gonna be a big man someday
[00:18.55] You got mud on your face, you big disgrace
[00:21.95] Kicking your can all over the place, singin'
[00:24.94] We will, we will rock you
[00:30.89] We will, we will rock you
[00:36.74] Buddy, you're a young man, hard man
[00:39.09] Shouting in the street, gonna take on the world someday
[00:42.03] You got blood on your face, you big disgrace
[00:45.34] Waving your banner all over the place
[00:48.38] We will, we will rock you
[00:53.25] Sing it out
[00:54.34] We will, we will rock you
[01:00.24] Buddy, you're an old man, poor man
[01:02.49] Pleading with your eyes, gonna make you some peace someday
[01:05.56] You got mud on your face, big disgrace
[01:08.75] Somebody better put you back into your place
[01:12.08] We will, we will rock you
[01:16.22] Sing it
[01:18.22] We will, we will rock you
[01:23.11] Everybody
[01:23.85] We will, we will rock you
[01:29.27] Hmm
[01:29.92] We will, we will rock you
[01:35.13] Alright
[01:35.94]
